       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. DRIVESVC.
       AUTHOR. OPENAI.
       REMARKS. DRIVER FOR INTEGRATION TESTS — CALLS SVCBILL001.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY POLDATA.
       01  RPT-LINE                 PIC X(160).

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN.
           PERFORM SEED-SVC-BILLING-MODE
           CALL "SVCBILL001" USING WS-POLICY-MASTER-REC
           STRING "SVC_BM_OK|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  PM-RETURN-CODE DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  "|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  PM-CONTRACT-STATUS DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  "|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  PM-BILLING-MODE DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  "|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  PM-MODAL-PREMIUM DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  "|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  PM-PREMIUM-DELTA DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  "|" DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  PM-SERVICE-FEE DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  INTO RPT-LINE
           END-STRING
           DISPLAY FUNCTION TRIM(RPT-LINE TRAILING)
           STOP RUN.

       SEED-SVC-BILLING-MODE.
           INITIALIZE WS-POLICY-MASTER-REC
           MOVE 20240601 TO PM-PROCESS-DATE
           MOVE "T1001" TO PM-PLAN-CODE
           MOVE "AC" TO PM-CONTRACT-STATUS
           MOVE 20220101 TO PM-ISSUE-DATE
                                 PM-EFFECTIVE-DATE
           MOVE 20240501 TO PM-PAID-TO-DATE
           MOVE 40 TO PM-INSURED-AGE-ISSUE
           MOVE 42 TO PM-ATTAINED-AGE
           MOVE "F" TO PM-INSURED-GENDER
           MOVE "N" TO PM-SMOKER-IND
           MOVE 1 TO PM-OCCUPATION-CLASS
           MOVE "ST" TO PM-UW-CLASS
           MOVE "A" TO PM-BILLING-MODE
           MOVE 25000000000.00 TO PM-SUM-ASSURED
           MOVE 500000.00 TO PM-TOTAL-ANNUAL-PREMIUM
           MOVE 450000.00 TO PM-GROSS-ANNUAL-PREMIUM
           MOVE 416666.67 TO PM-MODAL-PREMIUM
           MOVE ZERO TO PM-RIDER-COUNT PM-PREMIUM-DELTA
                     PM-SERVICE-FEE PM-OUTSTANDING-PREMIUM
           MOVE "BM" TO PM-AMENDMENT-TYPE
           MOVE "M" TO PM-NEW-BILLING-MODE
           .
